Talking out loud to myself helps me to gather my thoughts. And yes, I am in therapy every week. üòÇ 

Sometimes it feels like an uphill battle tbh and I get frustrated and wish I had a ‚Äúnormal‚Äù brain‚Ä¶but in life we get what we get and we gotta learn to accept and love our whole selves ..and learn how to deal with our quirks. Happy Monday to everybody on the struggle bus! ü•∞".
